<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7; padding: 20px; }
    .container { background: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
    .header { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    .info-row { margin: 8px 0; }
    .label { font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">New Job Application Submitted</div>

    <p>Hello HR Team,</p>

    <p>A new candidate has successfully submitted an application for:</p>

    <div class="info-row">
      <span class="label">Position:</span> {{jobTitle}}
    </div>

    <div class="info-row">
      <span class="label">Applicant Name:</span> {{name}}
    </div>

    <div class="info-row">
      <span class="label">Email:</span> {{email}}
    </div>

    <p>You can view the full application in the admin panel.</p>

    <br>
    <p>Best Regards,</p>
    <p>Career Portal</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
